intent: |
  Mid-engagement: two stakeholder groups disagree on scope. BA facilitates, captures positions, runs
  structured decision, records rationale for audit. Output: decision record + updated baseline +
  impact assessment.

scope: |
  Mid-engagement: two stakeholder groups disagree on scope. BA facilitates, captures positions, runs
  structured decision, records rationale for audit. Output: decision record + updated baseline +
  impact assessment.

summary: |
  Mid-engagement: two stakeholder groups disagree on scope. BA facilitates, captures positions, runs
  structured decision, records rationale for audit. Output: decision record + updated baseline +
  impact assessment.

